{"tid":1110974,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"宜家啲𡃁仔做乜野","createTime":"2019-04-16T18:44:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T19:03:55.000Z","uid":210284,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"89e002de4778d846db9eb6e5798a5db031a3d099","tid":1110974,"uid":210284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T18:44:10.000Z","msg":"唔講衣著，可能我呢個老野已經跟唔上潮流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得宜家嘅𡃁仔成咗年都係咁撚瘦削。<br />\n<br />\n有一日我見到有個Instagram account係個上身赤裸嘅𡃁仔，差唔多初中年齡，唔知佢係想搞笑定係點，瘦到得排骨都夠膽對住塊鏡影相黎做Icon，笑撚咗。<br />\n<br />\n另外，日日都見到附近啲學生走出嚟玩，玩係開心嘅，Ok冇問題，但係可唔可以唔好露後面腳筋出嚟，又係瘦到得返條筋，好似行下行下就會斷撚咗咁，件事好噁心。<br />\n<br />\n仲有，宜家啲𡃁仔剪嘅剪髮型愈嚟愈麒麟怪，唔知個頭想點，一大舊野咁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3be12fe7eca55152552c15d0ab59f40551801aca","tid":1110974,"uid":8534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T18:46:04.000Z","msg":"仲要對自己好有自信嗰下真係頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd28260a180242e788d3e2aa722b4d2ce13d5468","tid":1110974,"uid":210284,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3be12fe7eca55152552c15d0ab59f40551801aca","tid":1110974,"uid":8534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T18:46:04.000Z","msg":"仲要對自己好有自信嗰下真係頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T19:03:55.000Z","msg":"米臭係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾人打一拳就訓撚低個啲人"}]}